_sText:
This is just a simple, but betterlooking remake of ba_jail_electric_razor.

I always loved the gameplay, but hated the fullbright and the looks.


It's not an Edit - i made this from scrap.


This also includes:

x Pool
x Waterslide
x Soccer
x Disco
x Spraycontest Wall
x More Paths
x Secrets
x Randomly generated Secrets
x Hidden Weapons
x TopHATTwaffle's Daft Punk Soundboard


This is not a 1:1 Remake, so don't bother commenting with "OMG THIS ISNT THE SAME"
